  <brief_title>Management of Index Episode in Patients With Bipolar Disorder Treated by Seroquel XR</brief_title>
  <official_title>Non-interventional Study to obSERve currENt Management of Index Episode in Patients With Bipolar Disorder Treated bY Seroquel XR</official_title>
