  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary purpose of the study is to explore management of symptomatology in patients with
      bipolar disorder that experience a new manic,depressive or mixed episode and are treated with
      Seroquel XR monotherapy/adjuctive, in routine clinical practice in Romania
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
